name: MakeanImpact
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Is there a problem in your community that you wish you could help solve? Are you tired of sitting on the sidelines, unsure of what you could do to make the world into one you want to live in? Or are you already active in your community and you want to boost your impact? Kristin Alanna challenges you to have a growth mindset, giving inspiration, community insight, tips and strategies to help you Make an Impact! Enable this flash briefing to join changemakers on this social impact journey. For more updates, follow on Facebook: Kristin Alanna - Impact Knowmad. Together we have the capacity to influence positive social change, but always remember, the impact starts with you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
